{"type": "article", "id": 27614, "title": "多功能咖啡桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-01T06:57:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702143959JNZ2BdqLYMj8GIwx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>意大利设计师 Paolo D’lppolito 最近设计了一款多功能的咖啡桌 <a href=\"http://www.dippo.it/en/x-portfolio/prometeo-2/\">Prometeo</a>，矮小的桌腿使它很适合放在床上陪你一起惬意地休息。它采用一种名为 Adamantx 的新型材料制成，并且在表面做了抛光处理，看上去很有光泽。咖啡桌的表面有两个方型凹槽，可以放进配套的收纳盒还有钥匙、花盆等小物件。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143957fuLFExCXOH1iswtq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.90166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143957P6cbVpARFSQdnsHU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143958BoU1fdPiGjrCgtSJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143958CY7WXyFG8hTgENcv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}